    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>It's not like that. ArrayList just uses array as internal respentation. If you add more then 60 elements then underlaying array will be exapanded. How ever you can add as much elements to this array as much RAM you have.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 5889032,
      "reputation" : 8475,
      "user_id" : 4636217,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/Z4LYX.png?s=256",
