    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 9,
    "last_activity_date" : 1485790332,
    "creation_date" : 1485790332,
    "answer_id" : 41939670,
    "question_id" : 5600668,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Java 8 implementation <em>(List initialized with <code>60</code> zeroes)</em>:</p>\n\n<pre><code>List&lt;Integer&gt; list = IntStream.of(new int[60])\n                    .boxed()\n                    .collect(Collectors.toList());\n</code></pre>\n\n<ul>\n<li><code>new int[N]</code> - creates an array filled with zeroes &amp; length N </li>\n<li><code>boxed()</code> - each element boxed to an Integer</li>\n<li><code>collect(Collectors.toList())</code> - collects elements of stream</li>\n</ul>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 1716301,
      "reputation" : 2072,
      "user_id" : 1573292,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 61,
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/Wjlja.jpg?s=256",
      "display_name" : "BARJ",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/1573292/barj"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
